responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "8841F2664EFF035B6EA3A8B1A6BCDF92", "You\'re talking to a man whose days are numbered, my friend. How do I explain how a crop of goblins robbed me? They may be sick and weak, but they still manage to vex my nerves. I should tell you about the day they ambushed this very tower. The minute I get my hands on some siege, I\'ll send them flying right over the cliff there and into the depths of Foul Grog Lake.")
